marriage%20so%20far.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20Sepahijala%2C%20the%20numbers%20turned%20into%20faces.%20During%20voter%20verification%20drives%20and%20village%20visits%2C%20Jaiswal%20met%20girls%20who%20should%20have%20been%20in%20classrooms%20but%20were%20instead%20preparing%20for%20marriage.%20Some%2C%20barely%20in%20their%20teens%2C%20were%20already%20mothers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaiswal%20points%20out%20that%20Sepahijala%E2%80%99s%20diversity%20makes%20the%20challenge%20even%20more%20complex.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20tribal-dominated%20pockets%20and%20minority-heavy%20areas%2C%20each%20with%20distinct%20social%20norms.%20But%20across%20these%20communities%2C%20one%20alarming%20pattern%20cut%20across%3A%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F330387%2Fias-officer-district-magistrate-saju-vaheed-balika-manch-prevent-child-marriage-south-tripura%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprevalence%20of%20child%20marriage%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20teenage%20pregnancy.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%2C%20field%20assessments%20by%20his%20team%20revealed%20an%20even%20more%20disturbing%20pattern%3A%20girls%20as%20young%20as%2013%20were%20giving%20birth.%20This%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20a%20health%20emergency%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20a%20humanitarian%20and%20developmental%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20young%20girls%20were%20losing%20their%20futures%20before%20they%20even%20began%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20act%20now%2C%20our%20demographic%20dividend%20will%20become%20a%20demographic%20burden.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Jaiswal%2C%20the%20concern%20ran%20deeper%20than%20numbers.%20As%20a%20doctor%2C%20he%20had%20studied%20how%20child%20marriage%20fuels%20a%20cycle%20of%20malnutrition%2C%20infant%20mortality%2C%20and%20poor%20maternal%20health.%20He%20had%20also%20seen%20how%20cultural%20practices%20%E2%