dals%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekebabs%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20vegetable%20platters%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20journey%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F238392%2Flondon-halal-restaurant-usman-abubacke-owner-kerala-nri-chicken-tikka-masala-vindaloo-naan-poppadum-chutney-vid01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eideating%20an%20Indian%20menu%3C%2Fa%3E%20(heavy%20on%20spices)%20for%20a%20Brazilian%20audience%20%E2%80%94%20Brazilian%20cuisine%20hinges%20on%20bold%2C%20complex%20flavours%3B%20not%20so%20much%20of%20spice%20%E2%80%94%20was%20tough.%20Deepali%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20in%20Brazil%20love%20barbeques%2C%20heavy%20in%20herbs%20and%20salt.%E2%80%9D%20Catering%20to%20these%20palate%20preferences%20meant%20dialling%20down%20the%20spices%20in%20the%20Indian%20dishes%20while%20preserving%20the%20flavours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20an%20anecdote%20that%20puts%20into%20perspective%20how%20tough%20it%20was%20to%20procure%20Indian%20ingredients%20in%20Brazil%2C%20Vijay%20recalls%20their%20last%20supermarket%20rendezvous.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20found%20%3Cem%3Ejamuns%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20the%20market%20here%20only%20a%20few%20months%20back!%20We%20even%20clicked%20a%20picture%20with%20them%3B%20we%20were%20so%20excited.%20So%20you%20can%20only%20imagine%20when%20we%20started%20out%20in%202012%2C%20how%20tough%20it%20was%20finding%20the%20right%20spices.%20To%20preserve%20authenticity%2C%20we%20would%20make%20trips%20to%20India%2C%20and%20when%20friends%20would%20come%20visiting%2C%20they%20would%20bring%20us%20back%20%3Cem%3Ekasuri%20methi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(fenugreek)%20and%20%3Cem%3Echaat%20masalas%20%3C%2Fem%3E(spice%20powders).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20Deepali%20had%20to%20narrow%20down%20on%20two%20dishes%20that%20proved%20to%20be%20the%20most%20challenging%2C%20she%20says%2C%20it%20would%20be%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F347938%2Fbest-thatte-idlis-in-bengaluru-south-indian-breakfast-veena-stores-mavalli-tiffin-room-umesh-dosa-point%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Edosa%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Indian%20crepe)%20and%20%3Cem%3Eidli%20%3C%2Fem%3E(steamed%20rice%20cake)%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CClean%2C%20white%20%3Cem%3Eurad%20dal%3C%2Fem%3E%20(black%20gram)%20was%20not%20available%20in%20S%C3%A3o%20Paulo%3B%20whole%20%3Cem%3Eurad%20dal%3C%2Fem%3E%20was.%20To%20clean%20it%2C%20we%20would%20have%20to%20soak%20it%20for%20two%20days%20and%20then%20remove%20the%20black%20skin.%E2%80%9D%20%3Cem%3EGulab%20jamun%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Indian%20sweet%20made%20of%20milk%20solids)%2C%20too%2C%20was%20a%20task%20to%20prepare%2C%20as%20there%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20%3Cem%3Emawa%20%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20%3Cem%3Ekhoya%20%3C%2Fem%3Eavailable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20time%20Deepali%20finds%20herself%20at%20an%20impasse%20while%20ideating%20a%20recipe%2C%20she%20finds%20a%20way%20through%20it.%20And%20in%20that%20lies%20her%20success.%20Looking%20back%20at%20the%20journey%20to%20this%20point%20from%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmiddle-class%20Maharashtrian%20family%E2%80%9D%20to%20now%2C%20catering%20for%20the%20who%E2%80%99s%20who%20of%20the%20world%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20been%20telling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20two%20golden%20moments%20were%20added%20to%20her%20archives%20of%20culinary%20success%20when%20she%20catered%20for%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20at%20the%2018th%20G20%20Summit%20held%20in%20Rio%20de%20Janeiro%20in%20November%20and%20then%20once%20again%20at%20the%20XVII%20BRICS%20Summit%20in%20July%20this%20year.%20As%20Vijay%20smiles%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20with%20one%20prime%20minister%20and%20our%20journey%20led%20us%20to%20serve%20another%20too.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%20pictures%20courtesy%20Vijay%20Bavaskar%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1756801800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fupl